{
  "id": "adv_event_2506_01_01",
  "title": "星見プロ全国ツアー！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "三人でノートを覗き込んで、何を見ているんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "三人でノートを覗き込んで、何を見ているんだ？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 4.5000000954,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんの『やってみたかったリスト』を\n見せてもらっているんですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "さくらちゃんの『やってみたかったリスト』を\n見せてもらっているんですよ",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.6866668384,
      "endTime": 9.4427668254,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "普通のことしか書いてないから\n読んでも面白くないと思うけど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "普通のことしか書いてないから\n読んでも面白くないと思うけど……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 9.6494332631,
      "endTime": 15.648299630399999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-ai001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことありません！　さくらさんの人となりが\nうかがえて、とても興味深いです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そんなことありません！　さくらさんの人となりが\nうかがえて、とても興味深いです！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.8482998211,
      "endTime": 22.187846310799998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "やりたいことって、その人の個性が出ますよね～\nたとえば愛ちゃんなら「腹筋百万回やりたい」とか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "やりたいことって、その人の個性が出ますよね～\nたとえば愛ちゃんなら「腹筋百万回やりたい」とか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.3745131492,
      "endTime": 30.9539912223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ai",
      "speakerName": "小美山愛",
      "speakerNameEn": "小美山愛",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-ai.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-ai002.m4a",
      "text": "腹筋百万回かあ……まだやったことないけど\n出来るようになるといいな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "腹筋百万回かあ……まだやったことないけど\n出来るようになるといいな～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 31.1539910316,
      "endTime": 38.4026547431,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "ちなみに、{user}さんの\nやってみたいことってなんですか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "ちなみに、{user}さんの\nやってみたいことってなんですか",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.6159881909,
      "endTime": 42.645149214999996,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そうだな……星見市にいた頃は、星見プロのアイドル\n全員で全国ツアーをやれたらと夢見ていたが……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "そうだな……星見市にいた頃は、星見プロのアイドル\n全員で全国ツアーをやれたらと夢見ていたが……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.8518159389,
      "endTime": 51.5518155575,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "川咲さくら",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロで全国ツアー……それ、いいですね！\n私もやりたいです！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "星見プロで全国ツアー……それ、いいですね！\n私もやりたいです！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 51.7451488335,
      "endTime": 58.417620642900005,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "やれるものなら俺もやりたいが、売れっ子二十人の\n予定を合わせて全国各地を移動するのはさすがにな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "やれるものなら俺もやりたいが、売れっ子二十人の\n予定を合わせて全国各地を移動するのはさすがにな……",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.6042872905,
      "endTime": 66.5042871952,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_run-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 8113.332970900004
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "話は聞かせていただきましたわ！\nやる前から諦めるなんてらしくありませんわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "話は聞かせていただきましたわ！\nやる前から諦めるなんてらしくありませんわよ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 66.7176202614,
      "endTime": 73.8908402283,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "叶えたい想いがあるのなら、行動を起こすべきですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "叶えたい想いがあるのなら、行動を起こすべきですわ！",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 74.0775070667,
      "endTime": 78.82610116,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "赤崎こころ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
