      "text": "みんなと全国ツアーが出来るなんて夢みたいだよ\n楽しみだな～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "みんなと全国ツアーが出来るなんて夢みたいだよ\n楽しみだな～",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.0574164709,
      "endTime": 132.2260106404,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "俺も夢が叶って嬉しいよ。……まぁ、そのために\nこれからやらなきゃいけないことが山ほどあるんだがな",
      "translations": {
        "en": "俺も夢が叶って嬉しいよ。……まぁ、そのために\nこれからやらなきゃいけないことが山ほどあるんだがな",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 132.4393438976,
      "endTime": 140.51224114110002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "speakerNameEn": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01/sud_vo_adv_event_2506_01_01-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "普段のお仕事だけでも相当忙しいのに\n大丈夫なんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "普段のお仕事だけでも相当忙しいのに\n大丈夫なんですか？",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 140.698907884,
      "endTime": 146.0398147901,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
